<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Lucas Fernandes Roncolato">
  <section class="px-4 md:px-20 lg:px-0 lg:w-8/12 lg:mx-auto">
    <h1 class="font-bold text-3xl my-10 text-center">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-dark-grey">Last updated: 14/08/2024</p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Welcome to <span class="font-bold">Lucas Fernandes Roncolato</span>'s
      portfolio website. Your privacy is important to me. This privacy policy
      outlines how I collect, use, and protect your personal information when
      you visit my website. By using this website, you agree to the terms of
      this policy.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">2. Personal Data Collection</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      I collect and process the following personal data through the contact form
      on my website:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
      <li>
        <span class="font-bold">Name</span>: Collected to address you
        appropriately.
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="font-bold">Email Address</span>: Used to respond to your
        inquiries.
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="font-bold">Message</span>: Your message or inquiry details.
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mb-4">
      This information is collected solely for the purpose of responding to your
      inquiries and potentially discussing your project with you.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">3. Use of Data</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      The personal data collected through the contact form is used exclusively
      to:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
      <li>
        Respond to Inquiries: I use your name and email address to reply to your
        messages and discuss potential projects.
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mb-4">
      No additional analytics, tracking, or cookies are used on this website. I
      do not log IP addresses or collect data beyond what you voluntarily
      provide through the contact form.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">4. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Under the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), the legal basis I
      rely on for processing your personal data is:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
      <li>
        <span class="font-bold">Consent</span>: By submitting the contact form,
        you consent to the processing of your personal data for the purpose of
        responding to your inquiry.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">5. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      I do not share your personal data with third parties, except for the
      following:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
      <li>
        <span class="font-bold">Web3Forms</span>: I use Web3Forms to securely
        handle form submissions. Your data is sent directly from the form to my
        email via Web3Forms.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">6. Data Retention</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      I do not retain personal data longer than necessary. Your personal data
      will be kept only as long as needed to respond to your inquiry and, if
      applicable, to discuss or manage a project. After this period, your data
      will be securely deleted.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">7. Your Rights</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Under the GDPR, you have the following rights regarding your personal
      data:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
      <li>
        <span class="font-bold">Access</span>: You have the right to request a
        copy of the personal data I hold about you.
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="font-bold">Rectification</span>: You can request
        corrections to any inaccurate or incomplete data.
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="font-bold">Erasure</span>: You have the right to request
        the deletion of your personal data.
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="font-bold">Restriction</span>: You can request that I limit
        the processing of your data under certain circumstances.
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="font-bold">Objection</span>: You have the right to object
        to the processing of your data.
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mb-4">
      To exercise these rights, please contact me at: <a
        href="mailto:doublevisiondigitalinfo@gmail.com"
        class="text-blue-500">doublevisiondigitalinfo@gmail.com</a
      >.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">8. Security</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      I take appropriate measures to protect your personal data. The contact
      form submissions are handled securely by Web3Forms and sent directly to my
      email. However, please be aware that no internet transmission is
      completely secure.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">9. Governing Law</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      This privacy policy is governed by the laws of England and Wales. Any
      disputes arising in connection with this policy shall be subject to the
      exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of England and Wales.
